comments:
S: (pattern) ->
      return $(this.$$(pattern))
    nextword: ->
      random_idx = Math.random() * vocabulary.length |> Math.floor
      random_word = vocabulary[random_idx]
      {english, romaji, kanji} = random_word
      this.S('#englishword').text english
      this.S('#japaneseword').text romaji
    ready: ->
      this.nextword()
